title: Alpine - Wordpress Responsive One Page Parallax
description:
Alpine is modern professional and flexible one page parallax responsive multi-purpose WordPress theme, developed in 

Bootstrap framework with great attention to details. Theme can be used for any type of website: business, corporate, 

portfolio, products, marketing, etc. You can modify layout, styling, colors directly from within the backend.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/alpine-wordpress-responsive-one-page-parallax/7191059

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress
